  h4.display-4.text-primary
    | Spectrophotometry for Cell Growth Measurement
  ol
    li 3mL of cells are collected in every 15 minutes interval within 6 hours of incubation.
    li The samples are transferred into the spectrophotometer cuvette.
    li The cell growth is measured by the optical density (OD600).